### Payments — IndiHome inquiry→pay and GoPay top-up. Self-contained: run top to bottom.
### Transaction PIN (seeded): 123456.

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Source account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("accountId", response.body[0].id);
%}

### IndiHome bill inquiry → captures inquiryId (single-use, expires in 10 min)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/inquiry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biller": "INDIHOME",
  "customerNumber": "130001234567"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("inquiryId", response.body.inquiryId);
%}

### Pay the inquired bill (amount comes from the inquiry)
### Running it a second time → 400 INQUIRY_INVALID (single-use)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biller": "INDIHOME",
  "inquiryId": "{{inquiryId}}",
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "pin": "123456"
}

### Inquiry for GoPay → 400 INQUIRY_NOT_SUPPORTED (it is a direct top-up)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/inquiry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biller": "GOPAY",
  "customerNumber": "081234567890"
}

### GoPay top-up (direct — no inquiry; Rp10.000–2.000.000, fee Rp1.000)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biller": "GOPAY",
  "customerNumber": "081234567890",
  "amount": 50000,
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "pin": "123456"
}

### GoPay with an invalid phone → 400 INVALID_PHONE
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biller": "GOPAY",
  "customerNumber": "9999",
  "amount": 50000,
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "pin": "123456"
}

### GoPay below the minimum → 400 INVALID_AMOUNT
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "biller": "GOPAY",
  "customerNumber": "081234567890",
  "amount": 5000,
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "pin": "123456"
}
